    h1 Contacts List
    p Contacts lists indended to display list of personal people contacts.
    p Contacts list is a particular case of grouped <a href="list-view.html">List View</a> with one difference.
    p The only difference is what we nedd to add additional <code><b>contacts-list</b></code> class to the list view element (<code>&lt;div class="list"&gt;</code>)
